node.text:
Featuring three spectacular, award-winning home designs, the Edgeworth Collection offers single-level open-concept homes with covered patios, offices, and more. Ranging from 2,516 to 2,822 square feet, these exquisite home designs include 3 to 4 bedrooms, 2.5 to 3.5 baths, and up to 3-car garages. Edgeworth is located within the spectacular Ridgeline at Caramella Ranch master-planned community in South Reno, Nevada. Ridgeline is a short drive from Lake Tahoe and is located near world-renowned ski resorts including Mt. Rose, Heavenly, Squaw Valley, Northstar, Boreal, and Diamond Peak. 

Virtually tour and explore the Sarona home design on TollBrothers.com/NV. 
#LoveEverythingAboutHome

Encompassed by walking trails, parks, convenient commuter roads, excellent schools, and the growing Town of Prosper - this community also features rich amenities including a clubhouse and neighborhood swimming pool. To learn more and virtually tour the Maclean visit our website TollBrothers.com/TX.
